text:
At least seven people are believed to have contracted #COVID19 after voting in Wisconsin's primary election.

Voters and poll workers faced long lines due to reduced polling stations. Many did not have protective gear.

Some officials fear "this is just the beginning." https://t.co/33jSgHi6B6
